'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2875] on 1 November 2000 at 6:13:39 am'!"Change Set:		mvcToMorphicDate:			1 November 2000Author:			Bob Arning- when transitioning from mvc to morphic, do not send #displayWorldSafely to the ControlManager in world"!!Project methodsFor: 'menu messages' stamp: 'RAA 11/1/2000 06:07'!makeThumbnail	"Make a thumbnail image of this project from the Display."	world isMorph ifTrue: [world displayWorldSafely]. "clean pending damage"	viewSize ifNil: [viewSize _ Display extent // 8].	thumbnail _ Form extent: viewSize depth: Display depth.	(WarpBlt current toForm: thumbnail)			sourceForm: Display;			cellSize: 2;  "installs a colormap"			combinationRule: Form over;			copyQuad: (Display boundingBox) innerCorners			toRect: (0@0 extent: viewSize).! !